            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24822892">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">丞相末年，略不复省事，正封篆诺之。自叹曰：“人言我愦愦，后人当思此愦愦。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-26 16:15</span>
                  
                </p>
